{"tid":482421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑被偷拍裙底春　警嫂報案拉休班警長","createTime":"2017-11-28T06:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T08:17:39.000Z","uid":6647,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6bdb4b09b0db23dfd6fbe8a640f314a984318a94","tid":482421,"uid":6647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:56:33.000Z","msg":"油塘發生偷拍裙底疑案，休班投訴警察課男警長涉嫌游蕩被捕。昨午約5時半，一名年輕女子於大本型商場搭乘扶手電梯時，驚覺後方一名中年男子將手機低垂，鏡頭向上，懷疑他偷拍其裙底春光，連忙喝止對方及報警求助。 <br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場調查，在涉案男子手機內未有發現相關照片，以涉嫌游蕩將他拘捕帶署，並檢走其手機作進一步調查。據了解，被捕男子為一名休班警長，隸屬投訴警察課，而報案女子的丈夫亦是警務人員。由於案件涉及警務人員，案件交由觀塘警區重案組跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171128/bkn-20171128143522934-1128_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171128%2Fbkn-20171128143522934-1128_00822_001.html&d=tcLTG%2BufxrLO4M7QpfdgM8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ee372703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171128/bkn-20171128143522934-1128_00822_001.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n休班警又加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69570ce2505d0fd51c8cf3fa892583ff2a015f43","tid":482421,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"休班休班休班警<br />\n即係咩撚野身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa382d89d549a03693c69ba78c6fe59311e3c019","tid":482421,"uid":17641,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"阿Sir懷疑警嫂底褲收埋毒品，而家阿Sir嚴正執法都唔撚得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef769c4ab49ea9bcdde0696a016bb970e24e073","tid":482421,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"休班仲要警長 好波 !"},{"pid":"ffa3a756621427a5680d85312d1b4252eb7196fd","tid":482421,"uid":42850,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedB